        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-14 11:35:13.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI had already done some changes related to notification. But saw some changes related to notification were already pushed ye. But I had included these changes which are not available currently.\n\n1. Here I have sent the notification for starting, processing and Completed status (I refered \"5.3.3-1: General flow of VNF lifecycle management operations triggered by task resources\" in \"ETSI GS NFV-SOL 003 V2.4.1\").\n2. I have kept the prepareNotification seperately inside the corresponding lcm operation, so that we can add only the affected resources.\nfor example) for operate currently all vms are affected so we can add all the vms in affectedvnfcs, but for heal currently it is only one vm, so I would add only that VM info in affectedVnfcs.\nAnd I think the same would apply to many such parameter in notification request.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
